Lillian Porter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lillian_Porter 0 Lillian Porter (February 24, 1917, Alameda County, California – February 1, 1997, San Bernardino, California) was an American film and television actress. She retired after marrying Russell Hayden on July 11, 1946. They remained married until his death in 1981, but apparently the union was childless. She died in 1997, several weeks before her 80th birthday from undisclosed causes.
